'''花煎'''（{{lang|ko|화전}}）是一種[[朝鮮半島|朝鮮半島]]傳統的甜煎[[米餅|米餅]]，上面放有[[食用花|可供食用的時花]]<ref name="FIK hwajeon">{{cite web |url=http://www.foodinkorea.org/eng_food/korfood/korfood8_2.jsp |title=Ttuk, Hangwa : Kinds of Rice Cakes |work=Pan-fried Rice Cake |publisher=Korea Agro-Fisheries Trade Corporation |accessdate=2008-06-28 |archive-date=2008-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080123101322/http://www.foodinkorea.org/eng_food/korfood/korfood8_2.jsp |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last=Chʻoe |first=Sang-su |authorlink= |coauthors= |editor= |others= |title=Hanʾguk ŭi sesi pʻungsok |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Idc5AAAAMAAJ&q=hwajeon&dq=hwajeon&lr=&pgis=1 |year=1960 |month= |publisher=Kyŏnggi Taehak Minsokhak Yŏnʼguso : Koryŏ Sŏjŏk Chusik Hoesa |pages=54 |access-date=2008-10-02 |archive-date=2014-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630111136/http://books.google.com/books?id=Idc5AAAAMAAJ&q=hwajeon&dq=hwajeon&lr=&pgis=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[韓語|韓語]][[固有詞|固有詞]]又稱為{{lang|ko|꽃부꾸미}}、{{lang|ko|꽃지지미}}、{{lang|ko|꽃달임}}<ref name="EncyKorea">{{Cite web|url=http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pentry.html?s=K&i=263451&v=42 |title=화전 (花煎) |publisher=[[Empas|Empas]] / [[韓國民族文化大百科事典|韓國民族文化大百科事典]] |language=ko |accessdate=2008-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070321143002/http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pentry.html?s=K |archivedate=2007-03-21 }}</ref>。在不少傳統節日如[[上巳節|上巳節]]、[[重陽節|重陽節]]等都會食用。

==花煎遊戲==
[[File:Korean_Rhododendron_Rhododendron_mucronulatum_'Wheeldon_Pink'_Flowers.jpg|thumb]]
從[[高麗王朝|高麗王朝]]起，[[朝鮮族|朝鮮人]]在一些節日裡有玩「花煎遊戲」（{{lang|ko|화전놀이}}，{{lang|ko|花煎놀이}}）的傳統習俗，並會食用花煎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.aks.ac.kr/glossary/glossary_detail.asp?g_code=13545&page=1&c_code=&search_field=all&keyword=hwajeon&order=g_korean&kanada= |title=화전놀이 (花煎놀이), Hwajeon nori |publisher=[[韓國學中央硏究院|韓國學中央硏究院]] |accessdate=2008-06-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Ajo9a0gy?url=http://www.aks.ac.kr/glossary/glossary_detail.asp?g_code=13545 |archive-date=2012-09-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

每逢[[上巳節|上巳節]]，[[婦女|婦女]]就會帶著叫[[燔鐵|燔鐵]]（{{lang|ko|번철}}）的一種厚煎板<ref>[http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pimage.html?s=K&i=242450001&en=242450&p_i=&a_i=&e=1 ]</ref>去郊遊踏青，她們會採摘[[迎紅杜鵑|杜鵑花]]或其他盛開的花來做花煎，當中以杜鵑花煎（{{lang|ko|두견화전}}固有詞為{{lang|ko|진달래화전}}）最具代表性。花煎常會與加入同種[[花瓣|花瓣]]的[[花菜_(甜品)|花菜]]（{{lang|ko|화채}}，一種把[[水果|水果]]加入[[蜜糖|蜜糖]]水或[[五味子|五味子]]汁裡製成的朝鮮傳統[[甜品|甜品]]）<ref name="Eumcheongryu">{{cite web |url=http://www.foodinkorea.org/eng_food/korfood/korfood9_2.jsp |title=Kind of Eumcheongryu |work=Hwachae (Honeyed juice mixed with fruits) |accessdate=2008-06-28 |publisher=Korea Agro-Fisheries Trade Corporation |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080523091328/http://www.foodinkorea.org/eng_food/korfood/korfood9_2.jsp |archivedate=2008-05-23 }}</ref><ref name="Jindallae hwachae">{{cite web|url=http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pentry.html?s=K&i=263413&v=43|title=Jindallae hwachae (진달래화채 ──花菜)|publisher=[[Empas|Empas]]  / [[韓國民族文化大百科事典|韓國民族文化大百科事典]]|accessdate=2008-06-28|language=ko|archive-date=2007-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070321143002/http://100.empas.com/dicsearch/pentry.html?s=K|dead-url=no}}</ref>一同食用，例如以杜鵑花煎與[[杜鵑花菜|杜鵑花菜]]同吃。

到了[[重陽節|重陽節]]，人們也會舉行花煎遊戲，這時食用的花煎會以[[菊花|菊花]]瓣製作，亦即菊花煎（{{lang|ko|국화전}}），配以[[菊花酒|菊花酒]]（{{lang|ko|국화주}}）或[[柚子花菜|柚子花菜]]（{{lang|ko|유자 화채}}）。

==材料與變化==
除了杜鵑花煎和菊花煎外，任何可吃的時令花卉都可用作製造花煎<ref name="FIK hwajeon" />，例如[[春季|春季]]常見以[[沙梨|沙梨花]]製成的梨花煎（{{lang|ko|이화전}}）<ref name="FIK hwajeon" />、[[櫻花|櫻花]]煎（韓語固有詞：{{lang|ko|벚꽃화전}}）、[[堇菜|堇菜]]花煎（固有詞：{{lang|ko|제비꽃화전}}）。初夏時則多會食用[[薔薇|薔薇]]花煎（{{lang|ko|장미화전}}）<ref name="FIK hwajeon" />。[[雞冠花|雞冠花]]煎（韓語固有詞：{{lang|ko|맨드라미화전}}）則多在秋季食用<ref name="FIK hwajeon" />。

當沒有適合製作花煎的花時，會以[[水芹|水芹]]、[[艾草|艾草]]、[[石耳|石耳]]、[[紅棗|紅棗]]等做成花形裝飾放在煎餅[[麵團|麵團]]上<ref name="EncyKorea" />。

